This paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for edge learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper specifically focuses on the problem of retransmission decision in wireless data acquisition, which is related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The proposed protocol also involves measuring data uncertainty, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.LG, followed by cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.AI, and cs.SY.
